                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Vehicle power systems fall into four categories that procurement managers must match to their car charger specifications. <strong>Mismatching a 12V-only charger to a 24V truck causes immediate overvoltage failure</strong>, the #1 cause of fleet charger returns accounting for an estimated 12-18% of warranty claims according to WOWOHCOOL after-sales data across 200,000+ fleet units shipped.</p>
