                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">For fleet operators managing mixed vehicle types, wide-input (12-24V) GaN chargers eliminate the need for separate 12V and 24V SKUs, reducing procurement complexity by 50% and eliminating voltage mismatch returns entirely. Every WOWOHCOOL car charger undergoes 12V and 24V validation testing as part of the standard 4-stage QC process.</p>
